{"lastModified":1764149835557,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Aegean Sea, Greece\n\nShe accommodates up to 6 guests in 3 staterooms all en-suite.\n\nCharter our Shooting Star, a Gianetti 65 sailing yacht, throughout Greece. This elegant and modern yacht can accommodate six guests in three staterooms – a master cabin and two twin cabins (which can convert to double beds), all with en-suite facilities. Enjoy the ultimate sailing experience!","blueprint":{"name":"SHOOTING STAR","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::202c9040-b884-11ef-acbe-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2028e6c0-b884-11ef-acbe-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::202b7ed0-b884-11ef-acbe-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::20164920-b884-11ef-acbe-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::20260090-b884-11ef-a7ff-07a74832e51c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::20298300-b884-11ef-8f38-9db8e8a0107a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::20016190-b884-11ef-acbe-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::202d0570-b884-11ef-acbe-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1ff18310-b884-11ef-acbd-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::201537b0-b884-11ef-acbe-9fce5efdcc1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc245f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2027d550-b884-11ef-a